,"David J. Lagattuta","Ashish K. Meena","Harald Ebeling"],"categories":["astro-ph.CO"],"summary":"本文研究了双曲脐点(HU)奇特强引力透镜系统，通过参数化星系团质量模型在源平面绘制HU奇特像形成区域，并定义奇特共动体积(V_z<10)。在验证方法后应用于74个星系团模型，发现椭圆度与爱因斯坦半径或尖度组合最能区分高V_z系统，并估计每个星系团平均贡献约0.125个星系至其奇特体积，观测19个星系团有90%概率探测到至少一个HU系统。","date":"2026-07-01","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.31583","score":85,"stars":4,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"strong gravitational lensing","points":55},{"label":"pure cosmology","points":-30}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Strong Gravitational Lensing"]},{"id":"2606.31312","canonical_id":"2606.31312","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Dissecting the Obscured Core of GN20: an Active Galactic Nucleus Outshone by Young Stars","authors":["M. Hamed","L. Colina","P. G. Pérez-González","J. Álvarez Márquez","A. Crespo Gómez","L. A. Boogaard","A. Bik","H. Übler","S. E. I. Bosman","A. Alonso-Herrero","M. Perna","S. Arribas","L. Ulivi","M. Annunziatella","L. Costantin","A. Labiano","C. -L. Liao","C. Prieto-Jiménez","P. van der Werf","F. Walter"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA"],"summary":"通过对GN20（z>4处最亮的尘埃恒星形成星系之一）进行空间分辨的SED分解，发现AGN对星系整体能量贡献微弱（9%），但对其核心区域贡献显著（34%），表明JWST的高分辨率红外观测是揭示被恒星形成淹没的隐藏AGN的关键手段。","date":"2026-07-01","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.31312","score":85,"stars":4,"tier":"archive","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Dust and ISM"]},{"id":"2606.30711","canonical_id":"2606.30711","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Little Red Dots as Intermediate Mass, Super-Eddington Engines: Insights from Type IIn Supernovae and The 1837-1856 Great Eruption of $η$ Carinae","authors":["Rohan P. Naidu","Jorryt Matthee","Anna de Graaff","Alberto Torralba","Chris Ashall","Harley Katz","John Chisholm","Gabriel Brammer","Luc Dessart","Anna-Christina Eilers","Raphael E. Hviding","David O. Jones","Vasily Kokorev","Joel Leja","Hanpu Liu","Zhaoran Liu","Devesh Nandal","Pascal A. Oesch","Conor L. Ransome","Robert A. Si